{"tid":626134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（武術界阿源）真武館修道船","createTime":"2018-04-12T01:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T01:40:32.000Z","uid":63553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b21e1cba5d8587b5d581a48e3da27d1b846047c","tid":626134,"uid":63553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"自稱九秒內可打出一百拳，六年內實戰二千次，創立真武道的二十多歲年青武術家鄺啟源,網名修道船。<br />\n唔知修道船係2003年沉船之戰一役中戰敗後，經過15年既休養同訓練依家九秒可以打到幾多拳呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Yv8FsLmfKsE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYv8FsLmfKsE&d=Pwj1qcM7NItuKhpa9TTTitibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=7dc4ecbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Yv8FsLmfKsE</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/093956_e980224c7fc29ea54cfb21e8e5552c7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F093956_e980224c7fc29ea54cfb21e8e5552c7b.png&h=6c5940a2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}